column1: 2718~2164~The Range 2017~Zoom~~~21MZM1010~Zoom Power Stretch Compu-Backpack~21MZM1010~21M21MZM1010~Bags and Conference/Bag Brands | Bags and Conference/Computer Bags | Bags and Conference/Backpacks | Promotions/Conference Essentials | Brands/Zoom | ~Bags | Backpacks & Backsacks~Bag |  Bags |  Conference |  Brands |  Backpack |  Bag Brands |  Computer Bags |  Zoom |   |  Black / Charcoal~~FALSE~The Zoom Stretch Computer Daypack is the solution for those that stretch the limits of mobile tech.~Main compartment features padded laptop sleeve that fits most 17 inch laptop computers. The outside of the bag features a front iPad/tablet pocket that secures with elastic and side pockets with stretch mesh for quick access to all your mobile devices. The main compartment features a dedicated neoprene pocket for mobile power that will fit most  power solutions (not included).
